cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use VPP in academic work, please cite both this software and the accompanying paper."
title: "Verifiable Participant Points (VPP): an open-source blockchain ledger for survey participation credits"
abstract: >-
  VPP is an open-source system for recording survey participation
  credits as tamper-proof, pseudonymous transactions on the Base
  layer-2 blockchain. It consists of an upgradable smart contract, a
  stateless transaction-relay backend that covers all gas fees on
  behalf of students, and a React frontend with internationalised
  German and English UI.
